{"_path":"/councilor/service/s2067","_dir":"service","_draft":false,"_partial":false,"_locale":"","title":"「樂善里及長樂公園綠廊串連改善工程」地方說明會","description":null,"image":"/images/service/s2067-1.png","sequence":2067,"category1":"A. 健全都市發展","category2":"A.1 加速宜居城市建設","link":"https://www.facebook.com/share/p/18nMTnhCFc/","author":"李宗豪","head":{"meta":[{"name":"keywords","content":""},{"name":"robots","content":""},{"name":"author","content":"李宗豪"},{"name":"copyright","content":"© 2024 A7新林口-社區網站"},{"name":"og:title","content":"地方行政"}]},"publishedAt":"2025-07-31T00:00:00.000Z","toc":true,"body":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"樂善里及長樂公園綠廊串連改善工程地方說明會"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"「樂善里及長樂公園綠廊串連改善工程」地方說明會"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"今天召開「樂善里及長樂公園綠廊串連改善工程」地方說明會，感謝鄉親熱情參與。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"這個計畫是宗豪率先提案爭取，也感謝都發局爭取中央補助 1000 萬，計劃總經費約 2600 萬，現在終於一步一步進入實際規劃！"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"計畫將樂善國小旁、文德公園、長樂公園一帶零碎的綠地整合，改善內容包含三大方向："},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n1️⃣ 打造兒童遊戲場域.\n在南北側規劃「冒險型」及「親子型」兩種不同的公園，能探索、攀爬、滑行的動態空間，讓孩子盡情放電；也有沙坑、鞦韆等設施，適合幼齡孩童與親子共玩。"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n2️⃣ 行人動線優化.\n改善人行路徑，串連學校、公園與社區，讓大家走路更方便安全，也更適合散步、騎 YouBike。"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n3️⃣ 夜間照明營造.\n加強燈光設計，晚上也能有舒適安心的環境。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"今天很開心能和周邊居民、里長一起討論細節，也會把大家的建議帶回去持續追蹤！"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n大家有任何想法也歡迎留言告訴我，一起打造更好的生活環境！"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"s2067-1.jpeg","src":"/images/service/s2067-1.jpeg"},"children":[]},{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"s2067-3.jpeg","src":"/images/service/s2067-3.jpeg"},"children":[]},{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"s2067-2.jpeg","src":"/images/service/s2067-2.jpeg"},"children":[]}]}],"toc":{"title":"","searchDepth":2,"depth":2,"links":[{"id":"樂善里及長樂公園綠廊串連改善工程地方說明會","depth":2,"text":"「樂善里及長樂公園綠廊串連改善工程」地方說明會"}]}},"_type":"markdown","_id":"content:councilor:service:s2067.md","_source":"content","_file":"councilor/service/s2067.md","_extension":"md"}